---
import Base from "#/layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Google DSC SJEC Events">
    <section>
        <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row my-12 md:my-24">
          <div class="flex flex-col w-full sticky md:top-36 lg:w-1/3 mt-2 md:mt-12 px-8">
            <p class="ml-2 text-yellow-300 uppercase tracking-loose">Working Process</p>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-normal md:leading-relaxed mb-2">Working Process of GDSC SJEC</p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Hereâ€™s your guide to events conducted by GDSC SJEC
            </p>
            <a href="#"
            class="bg-transparent mr-auto hover:bg-yellow-300 text-yellow-300 hover:text-white rounded shadow hover:shadow-lg py-2 px-4 border border-yellow-300 hover:border-transparent">
            Explore Now</a>
          </div>

          <div class="ml-0 md:ml-12 lg:w-2/3 sticky">
            <div class="container mx-auto w-full h-full">
              <div class="relative wrap overflow-hidden p-10 h-full">
                
                  <div class="border-2-2 border-yellow-555 absolute h-full border"
                   style="right: 50%; border: 2px solid #FFC100; border-radius: 1%;">
                  </div>

                  <div class="border-2-2 border-yellow-555 absolute h-full border"
                   style="left: 50%; border: 2px solid #FFC100; border-radius: 1%;">
                  </div>
                
                  <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between flex-row-reverse items-center w-full left-timeline">
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-right">
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">23rd August, 2022</p>
                    <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Orientation Program</h4>
                    <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/orientation.jpg">
                    <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        A 15-minute fun interactive session with the juniors held at students square to make them join the community.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                  <div class="order-1  w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-left">
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">10th September, 2022</p>
                    <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">GDSC Launch</h4>
                    <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/launch.png">
                    <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        A formal session where we officially launch Google DSC SJEC. We also showed the website as well as the discord bot that we are developed.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between flex-row-reverse items-center w-full left-timeline">
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-right">
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">17th September, 2022</p>
                    <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Compose Camp</h4>
                    <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/compose-camp.png">
                    <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        This event introduces you to the Android App development using Compose. You will get an understanding of the content and pathways.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
                  <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                  <div class="order-1  w-5/12 px-1 py-4">
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-yellow-300">30th October - 4th November, 2022</p>
                    <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold  text-lg md:text-2xl text-left">REEL IT IN!</h4>
                    <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/reel-it-in.png">
                    <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        Do you have what it takes to be the content creator for Google DSC?! Let's put your creativity skills to the test!
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between flex-row-reverse items-center w-full left-timeline">
                    <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                    <div class="order-1 w-5/12 px-1 py-4 text-right">
                      <p class="mb-3 text-base text-green-300">Currently In Progress</p>
                      <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">Google DSC Recruitment</h4>
                      <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/recruitments.png">
                      <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        Do you wanna be part of the Google DSC team? Work and connect with the best in the college. Recruitments are here! Register yourself first by filling the form.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
      
                  <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
                    <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
                    <div class="order-1  w-5/12 px-1 py-4">
                      <p class="mb-3 text-base text-green-300">November 14th - December 14th, 2022</p>
                      <h4 class="mb-3 font-bold  text-lg md:text-2xl text-left">GCCP Campaign</h4>
                      <img src="https://gdscsjec.in/assets/img/events/cloud.png">
                      <p class="leading-snug text-opacity-100">
                        A Cloud Engineer plans, configures, sets up, and deploys cloud solutions. Join this campaign to get collection of on-demand courses, labs, and skill badges that provide you with real-world, hands-on experience using Google Cloud technologies.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Base>
